System prerequisites

	# Ubuntu/Debian
	sudo apt-get install libjpeg-dev zlib1g-dev

	# Mac OS X (via Homebrew)
	brew install libjpeg zlib


Installation of reportlab library

1) globally for the OS

	sudo pip install reportlab

then it will be possible to run script as:

	python createpdf.py /directory/path portrait

or

	python createpdf.py /directory/path landscape


2) using virtualenv

	sudo pip install virtualenv
	cd /some/dir
	virtualenv env
	source ./env/bin/activate
	pip install reportlab


then it will be possible to run script as:

	./env/bin/python createpdf.py /directory/path portrait

or

	./env/bin/python createpdf.py /directory/path landscape
